 an Indian accent by an American actor who plays Apu. Many other shows, like the Big Bang Theory, which involves an Indian character who cannot talk to women, perpetuates these stereotypes as well. %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
